"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-03-Chinese-audiences-flock-to-cinemas-to-watch-Paris-2024-live-1vLaUCy7yDu-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  As the Paris 2024 Olympics unfold, watching live broadcasts in cinemas has become a popular trend in China. Since the opening ceremony, cinemas have offered this service, allowing fans to cheer for Team China together. During Paris 2024, more than 800 cinemas across the country will broadcast over 20 sports live, including table tennis, badminton, diving and volleyball. The high-quality audio-visual equipment in cinemas enhances the viewing experience, providing an unparalleled way to enjoy the Games.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"